      "content": "i mean it's hard to call it a \"trade-off\" if the mining for wind parts is causing massive habitat destruction and water pollution in certain areas. feels like we're just trading one disaster for another. dont you think it's a bit misleading to just call wind \"clean\" when it has those kinds of impacts?",
